Step right into the Riptide, where everyone is embraced with open arms! Nestled in the charming Sunset neighborhood, this beloved spot had faced adversity when it was tragically burned down some years ago. But fear not, for it has been beautifully rebuilt, preserving the authentic spirit of San Franciscan happiness, and continues to serve as a cherished gathering place for the entire community. Discover the magic of live music and entertainment every night of the week, ensuring theres never a dull moment at the Riptide. Make sure to drop by and convey my warm regards with a big smile!
Took my hubby here for his 29th bday. He LOVED it. Both our 1st time here with a friend. Great venue STILL after the fire. Have yet to do karaoke or attend burlesque here. We cannot wait to return!

Had a blast at this place. My brother brought us here while we were visiting. We got to enjoy bingo night and had alot of fun. It was cool to learn about how they burned down an were rebuilt. If I lived in the area I could definitely see myself coming here alot. I especially enjoyed how we could get a pizza drop next door and eat it while drinking. Definitely a place to visit.

I recently visited The Riptide, a surf-themed bar in the Outer Sunset area of San Francisco, and I was blown away by my experience. This bar is located just blocks away from the beach, and the surf-inspired atmosphere is perfect for a relaxing evening out. The drinks at The Riptide are delicious and well-priced, and the staff and service are top-notch. The bartenders are knowledgeable and friendly, and they take the time to make sure youre happy with your drink. The service is fast and efficient, and the staff are always ready with a smile and a recommendation. The atmosphere at The Riptide is chill and inviting, with surf-inspired decor and a laid-back vibe. Theres plenty of seating indoors and when outside you get a perfect view of the beach. Whether youre looking for a place to grab a drink with friends, or just want to relax and unwind after a long day, The Riptide is the perfect spot. In conclusion, if youre looking for a surf-themed bar with great drinks, friendly staff, and a laid-back atmosphere, The Riptide in the Outer Sunset area of San Francisco is the place to be. I highly recommend this bar, and I will definitely be returning in the future. Five stars!
